text.__SUMMARY__: Prunus subglabra is a species of plant in the family Rosaceae. It is endemic to the Philippines.
text.Sources: Kalkman, C. (1998). "Prunus subglabra". The IUCN Red List of Threatened Species. IUCN. 1998: e.T37392A10044353. doi:10.2305/IUCN.UK.1998.RLTS.T37392A10044353.en. Retrieved 22 December 2017.
